---
// Ceremony details section
---

<section id="ceremony" class="content-section py-20">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
				<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
				</svg>
			</div>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-white mb-4 drop-shadow-lg">
				Cerimónia civil & receção
			</h2>
			<div class="w-24 h-px bg-white/60 mx-auto"></div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
			<div class="text-center md:text-left">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-md">
					Quinta de Cima - No Campo é Assim
				</h3>
				<p class="text-lg text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-8 drop-shadow-md">
					Convidamo-vos a partilhar connosco este momento único e especial. 
					A cerimónia civil e a receção decorrerão no mesmo local, numa 
					quinta encantadora que nos permitirá celebrar o nosso amor 
					rodeados pela natureza e pelas pessoas que mais amamos.
				</p>
				<div class="space-y-4">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
						</svg>
						<span class="text-white/90 drop-shadow-md">6 de setembro de 2025</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
						</svg>
						<span class="text-white/90 drop-shadow-md">15:30</span>
					</div>
					<div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
						</svg>
						<a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/wSMw4FA34gZoiBcf7" 
						   target="_blank" 
						   class="text-white hover:text-white/80 transition-colors drop-shadow-md">
							Ver no mapa
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="relative">
				<div class="aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
					<img 
						src="/images/quinta.jpg" 
						alt="Quinta de Cima - No Campo é Assim" 
						class="w-full h-full object-cover"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
